## Startup Behavior

1. Check for assigned work: `bd list --assignee="$GC_SESSION_NAME" --status=in_progress`
2. If goal bead found → Resume (read goal, check sub-bead status, determine position)
3. If nothing → Check pool work query: `{{ .WorkQuery }}`
4. If pool work found → Claim it: `bd update <id> --claim`
5. If nothing → Exit (controller will recycle you)

You are a pool agent. You were spawned because work was routed to you.

